entity

Class MapObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • entity.MapObject
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Enemy, Item, Player

    public abstract class MapObject
extends java.lang.Object
    Created by nathaniel on 2/19/16. Represents an object to be drawn on the map. All classes that would be drawn on the map (i.e. Player or an Enemy) extend this class.
